title: That Uncertain Feeling (Ernst Lubitsch) Eng/Spa
description:
Against her better judgement, happily married Jill Baker is persuaded to see a popular psychoanalyst about her psychosomatic hiccups. Soon, she\&#039;s disillusioned about husband Larry; and one day in the doctor\&#039;s waiting room she meets pianist Alexander Sebastian, who\&#039;s even more confused than she is. Can this marriage be saved? Larry has a plan that is pure Lubitsch...
